{"tid":2290433,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[試食有圖] 打冷小炒黃店 (內無精液太陽蛋)","createTime":"2020-11-18T04:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T23:26:20.000Z","uid":182895,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3291721c3ae0e5a5b43f5575439212622bd80adf","tid":2290433,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">(好啦我唔再講大渣哥隻神級透明精液太陽蛋了)</span><br />\n<br />\n話說真係好少黃店中菜, 特別係大排檔打冷檔, Wolipay 見到呢間所以去試下<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">平發潮洲館</span> </span><br />\n長沙灣元州街231-247號地下<br />\n<br />\nSummary: <br />\n1) 內外無高調黃 (個人覺得無問題) 主要做街坊生意五湖四海咩人都有<br />\n2) 電視係有線新聞同老細吹左幾句有屌鳩正苦 (睇返之前報道有屌過黑警) <br />\n3) 環境合格, 以同區小炒打冷都算係咁, 廁所算乾淨<br />\n4) 食物整體幾好, 價錢非常合理, 可再J<br />\n<br />\n圖<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">滷水拼盤加鵝片</span><br />\n滷水味剛好唔鹹, 鵝片無煮過龍, 雜併有幾件感覺浸得太耐, 豬腩肉非常Good J<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJypXgh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJypXgh.png&h=8fbcb4a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n椒鹽白飯魚<br />\n香脆無萬年油味, 粉漿唔錯, 無過鹹<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7LS6bA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7LS6bA.png&h=06b3660c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃花魚飯<br />\n鹹香十足, 油分充足, good J<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TZkvEs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TZkvEs.png&h=0ca4dc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煎馬頭<br />\n香口, 無過熟, 點少少豉油, good J<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LS00vEP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLS00vEP.png&h=f118bcec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳皮骨<br />\n老實講食唔到陳皮味, 不過幾香口, 鹹咗少少<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZYUz6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZYUz6X.png&h=b116d1ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒜蓉粉絲蒸勝瓜<br />\n重口味, 幾好食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xh4pcUh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxh4pcUh.png&h=4df3474a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煎釀虎皮尖椒<br />\n大大隻好抵食, 辣辣地good J<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yu5ottc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYu5ottc.png&h=458a7405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人頭$200-300 (狂食價)<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"bd4f51dc4304b14935b333cfdef02a9ea66cafbd","tid":2290433,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"打冷詩都好想意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111ffb58d503240e0d2933ca518de10a1fa89451","tid":2290433,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd4f51dc4304b14935b333cfdef02a9ea66cafbd","tid":2290433,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"打冷詩都好想意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"gogogo<br />\nbtw 呢到無金菇食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3e03af2ad2989149de1e1bebd6ced5a69b3f42","tid":2290433,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111ffb58d503240e0d2933ca518de10a1fa89451","tid":2290433,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd4f51dc4304b14935b333cfdef02a9ea66cafbd","tid":2290433,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"打冷詩都好想意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"gogogo<br />\nbtw 呢到無金菇食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji